  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个金融风控的RAG架构图。核心场景是：交易进入系统后，要先经过知识库检索相关案例，再送进大模型做风险评估。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那知识库这边我理解为需要两个模块：一个是账本服务做数据存储，另一个是专门的欺诈检测服务来做分块处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，LedgerService存原始交易记录，FraudDetection负责把数据chunk化。这两个要包在一个Knowledge_Base子图里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "chunk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Knowledge_Base子图画出来，里面放LedgerService和FraudDetection，标上Chunk & Process的流转关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "然后知识库要对外输出向量，连到PaymentGateway做嵌入存储。PaymentGateway在这里充当向量数据库的角色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "Generate Embeddings"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，Knowledge_Base到PaymentGateway的1b流程，Generate Embeddings。那交易入口呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "交易从TransactionQueue进来，先走2a流程生成embedding，然后2b去PaymentGateway做向量相似度搜索。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "Generate_Embedding",
        "Vector Similarity Search"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，Q到E是2a，E到DB是2b。不过这里有个问题——E节点你刚才说是FraudDetection，但知识库里已经有一个C也是FraudDetection？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "啊对，这是个问题。知识库里的C是处理历史数据的分块服务，外面的E是实时检测服务，虽然同名但职责不同。为了区分，外面的E保持FraudDetection，但我会用不同实例来理解。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，同名不同实例。那搜索完向量后，结果返回到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "PaymentGateway把检索到的相关chunks返回给CTX，CTX也是TransactionQueue的一个上下文实例，专门承载检索结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
