      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，DB到CTX标3号流程，Retrieve Relevant Chunks。接下来是组合阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
