    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，4a和4b两个Combine。原始交易队列Q和检索结果CTX，都要汇总到P节点，P也是TransactionQueue的聚合实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
