      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成，P到LLM是5号Send to LLM，LLM到R是6号Generate Response。整体检查一下：知识库子图、向量检索流、上下文组合、大模型推理，四层结构对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
